WEBVTT

00:00:01.396 --> 00:00:03.219
OWASP is a non profit

00:00:03.219 --> 00:00:06.564
that stands for the Open Web Application Security Project!

00:00:07.218 --> 00:00:11.511
OWASP is a community of developers, technologists and evangelists

00:00:11.511 --> 00:00:14.314
improving the security of software through:

00:00:14.782 --> 00:00:16.023
1. Tools and Resources	

00:00:16.366 --> 00:00:19.736
OWASP has 100+ active projects

00:00:19.736 --> 00:00:22.580
and new project applications are submitted weekly.

00:00:22.879 --> 00:00:24.346
Projects are open source

00:00:24.346 --> 00:00:26.604
and are built by our community of volunteers

00:00:26.985 --> 00:00:28.173
- people just like you!

00:00:28.477 --> 00:00:30.210
2. Community and Networking	

00:00:30.596 --> 00:00:33.704
There are hundreds of local chapters worldwide

00:00:33.704 --> 00:00:35.096
and thousands of members.

00:00:35.362 --> 00:00:38.464
Meetings are free and open to everyone.

00:00:38.464 --> 00:00:39.558
They include:

00:00:39.830 --> 00:00:40.642
● Training

00:00:40.642 --> 00:00:41.357
● Talks

00:00:41.357 --> 00:00:42.954
● And networking opportunities

00:00:43.673 --> 00:00:45.720
3. Education & Training

00:00:46.221 --> 00:00:49.012
OWASP hosts many events each year.

00:00:49.397 --> 00:00:50.973
They are a great way to:

00:00:50.973 --> 00:00:52.394
● Improve your skills

00:00:52.394 --> 00:00:54.162
● Build your professional network

00:00:54.162 --> 00:00:56.678
● And learn about new trends in the industry

00:00:56.940 --> 00:01:01.005
One of many ways you can get involved is to become a member!

00:01:01.283 --> 00:01:03.329
The membership benefits include:

00:01:03.850 --> 00:01:05.893
● Discounts for events and trainings

00:01:06.370 --> 00:01:08.781
● Your own OWASP email address

00:01:08.781 --> 00:01:10.794
and Google Workplace access

00:01:11.313 --> 00:01:14.465
● A vote in our OWASP Global Board elections

00:01:14.861 --> 00:01:18.533
And recently OWASP added a brand new member benefit!

00:01:18.735 --> 00:01:22.304
Access to hands-on application security training

00:01:22.304 --> 00:01:25.434
through the OWASP SecureFlag Open Platform!

00:01:26.282 --> 00:01:29.149
Join us and become a member today!

